  exact theorem7_5_p2_row_equilibration_le_sqrt_card_min_left_scalings
    hm A Aplus hrow
    ((ch7Op2LeftScaledCondSet_isLeast_iff_sum_abs_normalized
      hm A Aplus).mpr hmin)

/-- Theorem 7.5, `p = 2` row infimum form with the source full-row-rank side
condition discharged by an explicit rectangular right inverse witness
