/-- Problem 7.15 pointwise lower bound: every positive reciprocal two-sided
scaling has exact operator-2 condition value at least
`||A ∘ A_invᵀ||₂`. -/
theorem problem7_15_hadamard_op2_le_twoSidedScaledOp2Kappa_mem {n : ℕ}
